1
00:04:44,083 --> 00:04:48,750
Tonight we have
gathered here

2
00:04:48,999 --> 00:04:52,999
to do the Puja to
the Devi,

3
00:04:53,208 --> 00:04:55,875
that is Mahakali
- we can call Her

4
00:04:56,041 --> 00:05:00,583
or Durga.

5
00:05:01,125 --> 00:05:05,417
So many types of
forms She has taken,

6
00:05:05,709 --> 00:05:07,875
to kill

7
00:05:08,083 --> 00:05:13,917
the negative forces that
are trying to trouble

8
00:05:14,125 --> 00:05:16,750
or to obstruct,

9
00:05:16,999 --> 00:05:20,917
or even to grow

10
00:05:21,125 --> 00:05:25,792
the people who were

11
00:05:26,750 --> 00:05:30,458
gentle and good.

12
00:05:33,792 --> 00:05:36,834
Her forms are of
different types

13
00:05:37,041 --> 00:05:39,917
that we know about,

14
00:05:40,083 --> 00:05:44,500
that She destroyed
so many rakshasas,

15
00:05:44,750 --> 00:05:48,166
She destroyed so
many evildoers.

16
00:05:48,375 --> 00:05:50,750
Also we do not know

17
00:05:50,999 --> 00:05:54,625
that, in the World
Wars that we had,

18
00:05:54,875 --> 00:06:00,417
She was there to protect
the right type of people.

19
00:06:00,667 --> 00:06:03,959
And that’s how
they all survived

20
00:06:04,125 --> 00:06:07,999
the ill-blood plan,

21
00:06:08,208 --> 00:06:12,250
ill-gotten plan
of very cruel

22
00:06:12,500 --> 00:06:15,542
and evil people.

23
00:06:16,959 --> 00:06:20,834
The evil people have
a capacity to hate.

24
00:06:21,041 --> 00:06:26,834
And to express their hate in
every way that is possible.

25
00:06:27,375 --> 00:06:35,041
They are really born evil and
there are also who ‘become’ evil.

26
00:06:35,667 --> 00:06:39,583
When they are

27
00:06:40,625 --> 00:06:45,417
born evil, you can
make them out.

28
00:06:45,625 --> 00:06:49,709
That their whole style
is so aggressive,

29
00:06:49,959 --> 00:06:54,291
and so vindictive

30
00:06:54,542 --> 00:06:56,250
about things.

31
00:06:56,500 --> 00:07:00,333
But hatred has no limit,

32
00:07:00,583 --> 00:07:05,458
no limits at all.
Because, if they hate,

33
00:07:05,667 --> 00:07:09,083
if they hate someone,

34
00:07:09,333 --> 00:07:15,917
then, just to justify that hatred,
they’ll say all kinds of things.

35
00:07:16,083 --> 00:07:21,500
Just to justify. But sometimes
they don’t even want to justify.

36
00:07:21,750 --> 00:07:23,834
They just feel that
they ‘hate’

37
00:07:24,041 --> 00:07:27,834
and it’s a fundamental right
they have got to hate.

38
00:07:28,041 --> 00:07:33,458
But these forces join
together sometimes to form

39
00:07:33,667 --> 00:07:38,917
to form a joint
personality of evil,

40
00:07:39,083 --> 00:07:44,333
which tries to torture the
human beings and trouble them.

41
00:07:44,542 --> 00:07:49,792
They might take any name. They
might call them by anything,

42
00:07:49,999 --> 00:07:55,417
but they are absolutely
hundred per cent evil.

43
00:07:55,709 --> 00:07:57,834
and for such persons

44
00:07:57,999 --> 00:08:06,250
there’s no pity or compassion
from the God Almighty.

45
00:08:06,500 --> 00:08:08,875
These are to be
destroyed.

46
00:08:09,041 --> 00:08:11,583
And that is the job
of the Goddess

47
00:08:11,834 --> 00:08:18,000
to destroy them, who is a Mother,
full of compassion and love.

48
00:08:18,667 --> 00:08:23,208
It’s a very contradictory
work the Goddess has to do

49
00:08:23,458 --> 00:08:28,834
to kill these people, because, in
the larger interest, it is important

50
00:08:29,041 --> 00:08:36,500
that all such evil people
should be destroyed, completely.

51
00:08:36,792 --> 00:08:39,458
But they do not.

52
00:08:39,750 --> 00:08:43,542
They, like they go to jail for
some time. Like that, they

53
00:08:43,834 --> 00:08:45,875
go to hell for some
time, suffer

54
00:08:46,083 --> 00:08:48,792
and, again, they come
back much more strong

55
00:08:48,999 --> 00:08:54,583
and then again try to trouble
good saintly people.

56
00:08:54,834 --> 00:08:57,709
It’s a common style

57
00:08:57,917 --> 00:09:04,166
they are all over the world.
They can come in the form

58
00:09:04,458 --> 00:09:06,625
of a very good man,

59
00:09:06,834 --> 00:09:11,500
of a very gentle man, or of a
man who “knows a lot about God”

60
00:09:11,709 --> 00:09:15,834
or they can also say
that they can

61
00:09:16,125 --> 00:09:18,625
give you Realisation.

62
00:09:18,999 --> 00:09:22,458
All kinds of lies
they are capable of,

63
00:09:22,792 --> 00:09:28,250
because they have that power
evil, power of doing evil.

64
00:09:28,458 --> 00:09:31,542
So they take to all
kinds of falsehood

65
00:09:31,750 --> 00:09:35,500
and they proclaim that:
“We are this and we are that,”

66
00:09:35,750 --> 00:09:40,208
and “ We can give
you this or that.”

67
00:09:41,291 --> 00:09:45,208
Actually, they have come on
this Earth to ruin people.

68
00:09:45,458 --> 00:09:48,625
We’ve had many of
these false people

69
00:09:48,875 --> 00:09:52,125
and many stupid
people followed them.

70
00:09:52,333 --> 00:09:55,417
They never talked
against each other.

71
00:09:55,667 --> 00:09:59,667
Christ has said that,

72
00:10:00,125 --> 00:10:03,667
“The devil won’t talk
against its own house.”

73
00:10:03,959 --> 00:10:08,166
As if they are in ‘one’ house.
And in ‘one’ house they live

74
00:10:08,417 --> 00:10:10,250
and they cannot talk,

75
00:10:10,458 --> 00:10:16,417
they cannot talk
of something

76
00:10:16,667 --> 00:10:20,875
that may disturb their
collectivity or their fraternity.

77
00:10:21,083 --> 00:10:24,667
The fraternity is so
great that,

78
00:10:24,875 --> 00:10:27,792
wherever they are,
they ‘know’

79
00:10:28,041 --> 00:10:32,834
that they are together.
Just imagine.

80
00:10:33,041 --> 00:10:35,999
all the evil people
should join together

81
00:10:36,208 --> 00:10:40,417
and behave in this manner
is very surprising.

82
00:10:40,792 --> 00:10:42,792
That way, they are
very collective.

83
00:10:43,000 --> 00:10:48,583
Supposing one has taken a
particular part of the land,

84
00:10:48,875 --> 00:10:52,250
then he dominates there. Another
takes up in another way.

85
00:10:52,458 --> 00:10:55,625
Third one takes. There’s
no competition as such.

86
00:10:55,959 --> 00:10:59,458
Ultimate effort is, somehow
or other,

87
00:10:59,750 --> 00:11:03,917
to destroy all the
creation of God,

88
00:11:04,125 --> 00:11:06,166
all the good people
of the world,

89
00:11:06,375 --> 00:11:12,041
who will ultimately get
their Self-Realisation

90
00:11:12,250 --> 00:11:18,125
and who will have the
Knowledge about Reality.

91
00:11:19,000 --> 00:11:25,250
This kind of atmosphere is
the worst during Kali Yuga

92
00:11:25,542 --> 00:11:28,834
and there are so many
stupid, stupid people,

93
00:11:29,083 --> 00:11:32,041
who may be simple, who
may be good-natured,

94
00:11:32,333 --> 00:11:37,291
but they get drawn by the
evil doing of these people,

95
00:11:37,667 --> 00:11:41,709
while the good people
also sometimes

96
00:11:41,959 --> 00:11:46,250
follow suite. They also try to
follow them. It’s very surprising.

97
00:11:46,500 --> 00:11:51,000
Why should good people not under-
stand what is good and what is bad?

98
00:11:51,208 --> 00:11:54,500
But, that discrimination,
many good people also lack

99
00:11:54,750 --> 00:11:57,625
and that’s why they
take to wrong things.

100
00:11:57,875 --> 00:12:00,834
And then they go on
justifying all the time

101
00:12:01,000 --> 00:12:03,542
whatever they are doing
is the right thing,

102
00:12:03,750 --> 00:12:08,083
is the best thing, they
have the proof of it.

103
00:12:09,291 --> 00:12:14,083
Now, as you know, there has
been many of them in Kali Yuga

104
00:12:14,333 --> 00:12:19,875
and so many of them have now
disappeared from this Earth

105
00:12:20,250 --> 00:12:25,750
and now they cannot trouble us.
But there are still some more,

106
00:12:26,041 --> 00:12:28,041
who are exposed.

107
00:12:28,291 --> 00:12:32,250
People have exposed
them so much

108
00:12:32,500 --> 00:12:35,500
that nobody can expose

109
00:12:35,959 --> 00:12:39,917
anybody without any proof.

110
00:12:40,125 --> 00:12:42,166
But they have such courage

111
00:12:42,375 --> 00:12:46,375
and they are so
full of confidence

112
00:12:46,625 --> 00:12:49,917
that they can do
what they like,

113
00:12:50,083 --> 00:12:52,583
and anybody tries
to expose them,

114
00:12:52,792 --> 00:12:56,667
they will definitely
ruin that person.

115
00:12:56,999 --> 00:12:59,125
A few things they
are doing.

116
00:12:59,375 --> 00:13:03,834
First of all, they put wrong
ideas into your head.

117
00:13:04,125 --> 00:13:07,125
They say that:
"We are very

118
00:13:07,333 --> 00:13:10,667
great people we are this, we
are that. God has sent us."

119
00:13:10,875 --> 00:13:12,667
All sorts of things they will talk.

120
00:13:12,917 --> 00:13:15,458
But there is no proof
about it.

121
00:13:15,667 --> 00:13:18,792
And human beings never
ask for the proof,

122
00:13:18,999 --> 00:13:21,458
as to: “How do you say?

123
00:13:21,667 --> 00:13:23,667
What is the proof? ”

124
00:13:23,959 --> 00:13:27,000
So the solution is
the Sahaja Yoga.

125
00:13:27,291 --> 00:13:32,291
In Sahaja Yoga, you have
the experience. You have the proof.

126
00:13:32,542 --> 00:13:35,458
Then you grow into it.

127
00:13:35,709 --> 00:13:39,709
Immediately you cannot be a great
Sahaja Yogi, that’s a fact.

128
00:13:39,959 --> 00:13:42,041
You have to mature.

129
00:13:42,291 --> 00:13:44,458
It takes some time
for some people.

130
00:13:44,667 --> 00:13:47,917
It takes some more time for
other people. It doesn’t matter.

131
00:13:48,208 --> 00:13:50,083
But you do mature.

132
00:13:50,291 --> 00:13:53,875
In the meanwhile, if you try
to go to these wrong people,

133
00:13:54,041 --> 00:13:56,458
then there is
no possibility,

134
00:13:56,750 --> 00:14:00,250
there’s no way of
again bringing you up.

135
00:14:00,458 --> 00:14:03,959
Especially those people who rise
high in Sahaja Yoga, I think.

136
00:14:04,125 --> 00:14:07,917
If they fall,
they fall so low.

137
00:14:08,166 --> 00:14:11,000
Then even an ordinary
Sahaja Yogi

138
00:14:11,208 --> 00:14:14,500
could say: “ Mother, look at him!
Where has he gone?”

139
00:14:14,834 --> 00:14:18,792
So, with all these
things happening,

140
00:14:20,000 --> 00:14:24,166
what is our job

141
00:14:24,709 --> 00:14:27,959
is to worship
Mahakali within us.

142
00:14:28,208 --> 00:14:32,875
Because, what does She do?
Perhaps we are not very aware of.

143
00:14:33,250 --> 00:14:38,208
First and foremost thing
She does is to protect us.

144
00:14:38,458 --> 00:14:42,667
Wherever you may be,
whatever you may be doing,

145
00:14:42,875 --> 00:14:45,875
in whatever peril you
may be,

146
00:14:46,125 --> 00:14:50,250
howsoever dangerously you
may be placed in life,

147
00:14:50,500 --> 00:14:54,500
She protects you. First
thing, She protects you.

148
00:14:54,750 --> 00:14:58,166
All the people who write to
Me, how they were protected,

149
00:14:58,375 --> 00:15:01,709
how they were cured,
how they were helped.

150
00:15:01,959 --> 00:15:04,542
It’s this thing: that
they should know

151
00:15:04,750 --> 00:15:10,250
that all this has happened because
of Mahakali power within you.

152
00:15:10,625 --> 00:15:12,875
She exists within you.

153
00:15:13,083 --> 00:15:14,999
When you are
worshipping Mahakali,

154
00:15:15,166 --> 00:15:17,583
you are worshipping the
Mahakali ‘within you’.

155
00:15:17,792 --> 00:15:19,792
With due respect,
you must know

156
00:15:19,999 --> 00:15:23,417
that this Mahakali is a
very sensitive personality.

157
00:15:23,709 --> 00:15:25,999
She is very sensitive.

158
00:15:26,250 --> 00:15:30,834
If you try to do any
wrong to anyone,

159
00:15:31,291 --> 00:15:34,875
She’ll guide you. She’ll tell
you by many ways

160
00:15:35,041 --> 00:15:36,417
that: "This is wrong what
you are doing.

161
00:15:36,625 --> 00:15:39,417
Why are you doing wrong
to some person?”

162
00:15:39,792 --> 00:15:41,792
But if you do not repent

163
00:15:41,999 --> 00:15:46,375
and come back onto the normal
position, She gives you up.

164
00:15:46,959 --> 00:15:51,458
Once Mahakali gives you
up, you are now exposed

165
00:15:51,709 --> 00:15:55,834
and become prone to all
kinds of evil things.

166
00:15:56,041 --> 00:15:58,500
I would say…

167
00:16:01,667 --> 00:16:04,792
“What’s the matter
with the baby?”

168
00:16:26,625 --> 00:16:29,208
So, when you worship
Her, what do you want?

169
00:16:29,417 --> 00:16:34,709
You want Her to protect you.
In your discrimination,

170
00:16:34,999 --> 00:16:39,417
in your mistake, you might
do something wrong.

171
00:16:39,667 --> 00:16:43,792
May do something that
is not good for you,

172
00:16:44,000 --> 00:16:46,875
could be very dangerous
for you.

173
00:16:47,125 --> 00:16:50,208
But She is the person
who guides

174
00:16:50,417 --> 00:16:52,583
how to avoid all
the dangers.

175
00:16:53,834 --> 00:16:57,500
Now, She protects
your life,

176
00:16:57,750 --> 00:16:59,750
She protects your body,

177
00:16:59,999 --> 00:17:02,999
She protects all organs
of your body,

178
00:17:03,208 --> 00:17:08,250
She is the One who gives you
all the security of life.

179
00:17:09,250 --> 00:17:14,625
In Her realm, you feel
completely secure.

180
00:17:14,917 --> 00:17:17,667
You are never afraid
of anything.

181
00:17:17,917 --> 00:17:21,625
Because you have left Her
realm, you have come out of it,

182
00:17:21,834 --> 00:17:24,917
that is why, that is the
reason you are afraid.

183
00:17:25,083 --> 00:17:29,917
But if you are under
Her beautiful

184
00:17:30,125 --> 00:17:32,959
guidance and Her
blessings,

185
00:17:33,166 --> 00:17:36,417
you will never feel
afraid to do anything.

186
00:17:36,834 --> 00:17:39,166
You will never do
anything wrong also.

187
00:17:39,375 --> 00:17:43,208
As soon as you’ll try to do
wrong, She will hold your hand.

188
00:17:43,500 --> 00:17:46,000
She is really the
guiding person.

189
00:17:46,250 --> 00:17:50,250
She is the One who actually
gives us our existence.

190
00:17:50,542 --> 00:17:55,125
Without Her, we
cannot exist, because

191
00:17:55,542 --> 00:18:02,959
She is the One who is
the Power of Shri Shiva.

192
00:18:05,250 --> 00:18:09,375
She gives us so many things.
For example,

193
00:18:09,625 --> 00:18:15,917
She gives us the
relaxation, the sleep.

194
00:18:16,250 --> 00:18:18,542
She gives you the Truth.

195
00:18:18,999 --> 00:18:21,625
She tells you what is the
Truth and what is not.

196
00:18:21,875 --> 00:18:23,250
Sometimes people

197
00:18:23,500 --> 00:18:26,875
so much in their ego
always try to believe that:

198
00:18:27,041 --> 00:18:28,750
“What I think is
the truth.”

199
00:18:28,959 --> 00:18:35,041
Then She is the One who points
it out by creating a ‘Maya’,

200
00:18:35,291 --> 00:18:39,291
a kind of a confusion,

201
00:18:39,625 --> 00:18:42,999
that you start thinking:
“What is this?”

202
00:18:43,208 --> 00:18:48,625
So She is called also the One who
gives us ‘Bhranti,’ means illusions.

203
00:18:48,875 --> 00:18:52,083
She puts you to illusions
also. She tells you

204
00:18:52,333 --> 00:18:54,875
puts you to illusions
and She

205
00:18:55,041 --> 00:18:58,625
then ultimately takes you
out of the illusions.

206
00:18:59,291 --> 00:19:01,458
She is the One who
relaxes you,

207
00:19:01,709 --> 00:19:05,041
because She takes over all
your responsibilities.

208
00:19:05,291 --> 00:19:07,500
She takes over all
your problems.

209
00:19:07,750 --> 00:19:09,959
She is the One who
solves all the problems.

210
00:19:10,125 --> 00:19:14,500
It is we who forget to leave
all the problems to Her.

211
00:19:14,750 --> 00:19:19,709
If you just leave problems to Her,
all your problems are solved.

212
00:19:19,959 --> 00:19:23,709
Not only that, but you
really feel blessed.

213
00:19:23,999 --> 00:19:28,166
It’s not only physical,
also it is mental

214
00:19:28,417 --> 00:19:32,834
that She makes your mind
absolutely free of worries.

215
00:19:33,041 --> 00:19:37,583
She doesn’t worry and She
doesn’t want you to worry.

216
00:19:37,834 --> 00:19:40,667
If you worry, then
She tries to show that,

217
00:19:40,875 --> 00:19:44,083
by your worry,
you are denying Her.

218
00:19:44,417 --> 00:19:46,709
You are not accepting Her.

219
00:19:46,999 --> 00:19:49,125
Worrying is something
very common

220
00:19:49,375 --> 00:19:51,041
and people take great
pride in saying:

221
00:19:51,291 --> 00:19:52,542
“Oh, I was worried.”

222
00:19:52,750 --> 00:19:57,542
How can you be worried when your
Mother is “Sakshat Mahakali”.

223
00:19:57,875 --> 00:20:01,500
She can kill all the demons.
She can finish all of them.

224
00:20:01,750 --> 00:20:03,458
She knows how
to manage things.

225
00:20:03,709 --> 00:20:06,750
And when you are like
a child before Her,

226
00:20:06,999 --> 00:20:09,333
how can you worry
about anything?

227
00:20:09,542 --> 00:20:12,125
So your worries
are finished.

228
00:20:12,417 --> 00:20:15,417
She worries about you, you
shouldn’t worry about yourself.

229
00:20:15,667 --> 00:20:20,333
That’s the point of it. Her
security is so great,

230
00:20:20,542 --> 00:20:23,709
She is so secure
Herself, that

231
00:20:23,917 --> 00:20:27,959
She gives you all the
security that you need.

232
00:20:28,208 --> 00:20:30,792
You can hold on
to Her feet.

233
00:20:30,999 --> 00:20:35,250
You can hold on to Her
image or to anything.

234
00:20:35,542 --> 00:20:37,417
You can even pray to Her.

235
00:20:37,625 --> 00:20:41,709
Many people are being cured
only by praying to Her.

236
00:20:41,959 --> 00:20:43,917
Because She cures you.

237
00:20:44,166 --> 00:20:46,083
She can cure your
diseases,

238
00:20:46,333 --> 00:20:49,999
which are very complicated
diseases. She can cure.

239
00:20:50,375 --> 00:20:55,250
Now what She likes ?
Mahakali likes the light.

240
00:20:55,792 --> 00:20:59,959
She is worshipped in the night,
because then we can put on the light.

241
00:21:00,458 --> 00:21:03,291
She likes enlightened
persons.

242
00:21:03,500 --> 00:21:07,999
Also She likes the light.
She likes the Sun. She likes,

243
00:21:08,166 --> 00:21:13,667
something that will be completely
enlightened and brightened.

244
00:21:14,625 --> 00:21:19,041
You must have heard about people
who are called… I don’t know what,

