gather round a person,

484
00:36:48,625 --> 00:36:52,542
because, I think, there’s a
subtle ego of their money,

485
00:36:52,792 --> 00:36:56,166
that: “We can afford to
buy this, buy that.”

486
00:36:56,667 --> 00:37:01,125
Once I was in America and there
was one lady who came to see Me

487
00:37:01,375 --> 00:37:05,583
and she didn’t know that I
was… a spiritual person.

488
00:37:05,834 --> 00:37:10,250
So she said: “Now there’s a very
good guru who has come to America.”

489
00:37:10,542 --> 00:37:12,083
I said: “Really?
What does he do?

490
00:37:12,375 --> 00:37:15,917
She said: “There’s a sale
on.” I said: “Really?”

491
00:37:16,208 --> 00:37:19,500
“You can pay him
half the amount:

492
00:37:19,792 --> 00:37:23,000
he can give you his blessings.
Alright?”

493
00:37:23,250 --> 00:37:27,709
Then next week, she said: “Now
the sale has come to one fourth.

494
00:37:27,999 --> 00:37:30,208
If you pay the one
fourth amount,

495
00:37:30,417 --> 00:37:32,875
then he will give you
the ‘full’ knowledge.”

496
00:37:33,041 --> 00:37:35,667
I said: “How can
it be reciprocal?

497
00:37:35,875 --> 00:37:38,041
It’s not proportionate!”
I said:

498
00:37:38,291 --> 00:37:41,417
“You were giving half,
he was giving you half,

499
00:37:41,625 --> 00:37:43,667
and when you are giving
one-fourth, he is giving you full.”

500
00:37:43,917 --> 00:37:45,542
“That’s the thing”
she said,

501
00:37:45,750 --> 00:37:49,917
“he’s very magnanimous, you see.
That’s the point.”

502
00:37:50,417 --> 00:37:55,417
I said: “For all such people who
think they can purchase Truth,

503
00:37:55,667 --> 00:37:59,999
they cannot achieve it.
You cannot purchase it.

504
00:38:00,792 --> 00:38:05,083
You cannot pay for your
Kundalini awakening. No!

505
00:38:05,417 --> 00:38:08,250
Nor you should take any
payment for that.

506
00:38:08,500 --> 00:38:14,166
Self-Realisation is
absolutely the Divine Grace.

507
00:38:14,458 --> 00:38:18,375
And you cannot take
money for that.

508
00:38:19,166 --> 00:38:23,208
You cannot sell it. It’s not
so ‘cheap’ to be sold.

509
00:38:23,500 --> 00:38:28,834
If you understand that, then
the Mahalakshmi power works.

510
00:38:29,166 --> 00:38:31,041
And Mahalakshmi power is

511
00:38:31,291 --> 00:38:34,542
really meant for people who
are really genuine seekers,

512
00:38:34,834 --> 00:38:39,917
who are really seeking genuinely.
It acts and works so well,

513
00:38:40,166 --> 00:38:45,291
that they achieve a
kind of a very, very

514
00:38:45,583 --> 00:38:48,709
spontaneous Realisation.

515
00:38:49,166 --> 00:38:53,166
This spontaneous Realisation,
you all have got it.

516
00:38:53,458 --> 00:38:57,500
You don’t have to go to Himalayas. You
don’t have to do anything like that.

517
00:38:57,709 --> 00:39:01,999
All those things are over.
You have done it.

518
00:39:02,250 --> 00:39:04,792
In your previous lives,
you must have done it.

519
00:39:04,999 --> 00:39:06,542
Now you don’t have
to do anything.

520
00:39:06,792 --> 00:39:10,875
You can get it, you are getting
it just sitting down here.

521
00:39:11,083 --> 00:39:14,375
Wherever you are in the
whole world, you can get it

522
00:39:14,625 --> 00:39:16,500
and it is spreading
very fast.

523
00:39:16,709 --> 00:39:23,041
Now, it’s also the duty of Sahaja
Yogis to spread Sahaja Yoga.

524
00:39:24,041 --> 00:39:27,999
Now, this one is

525
00:39:28,208 --> 00:39:32,333
to be understood: that
Mahalakshmi and Mahakali

526
00:39:32,667 --> 00:39:36,417
both go hand in hand.

527
00:39:36,667 --> 00:39:40,917
When, you see,
Mahakali blesses you

528
00:39:41,125 --> 00:39:44,667
and She is with you and
you are in Her realm,

529
00:39:44,875 --> 00:39:46,792
the Mahalakshmi comes
forward

530
00:39:46,999 --> 00:39:50,709
and She definitely helps you
to achieve your Realisation

531
00:39:50,959 --> 00:39:55,250
and also to improve
your problems,

532
00:39:55,458 --> 00:39:59,417
to help you. I mean - the financial
side of it, you can call it,

533
00:39:59,667 --> 00:40:01,375
or in any way other

534
00:40:01,583 --> 00:40:05,709
problems also She solves. The
greatest problem She solves

535
00:40:05,917 --> 00:40:11,625
that your greatest desire to achieve
Self-Realisation, is granted.

536
00:40:12,041 --> 00:40:15,125
So, there is no competition
between Them.

537
00:40:15,417 --> 00:40:18,959
All these three powers
work together,

538
00:40:19,166 --> 00:40:22,999
and, whatever is needed,
they work it out.

539
00:40:23,250 --> 00:40:28,875
But it is the Mahakali who
guides where what help has to go

540
00:40:29,083 --> 00:40:34,375
and that’s why the power of
Mahakali is very much respected.

541
00:40:34,625 --> 00:40:41,041
As it is, She has killed so many
devils and so many rakshasas

542
00:40:41,291 --> 00:40:44,999
and there are still more –
some of them are existing

543
00:40:45,166 --> 00:40:47,291
but I am sure they
will be all finished.

544
00:40:47,500 --> 00:40:53,166
There will be none of these
horrible ones ever existing.

545
00:40:53,417 --> 00:40:57,917
But still we have to be
very careful and alert

546
00:40:58,083 --> 00:41:01,583
and try to find out what’s
wrong with these people.

547
00:41:01,792 --> 00:41:06,875
What are they doing and what
they trying to propagate?

548
00:41:07,083 --> 00:41:10,999
You must mature in
such a manner that

549
00:41:11,208 --> 00:41:16,333
you should know everything
of all these evil doers.

550
00:41:16,583 --> 00:41:20,417
You must find out what these
false people are doing.

551
00:41:20,625 --> 00:41:24,542
See, it’s really easy, because
you are enlightened.

552
00:41:24,792 --> 00:41:28,875
And with your enlightened attention,
you can definitely find out

553
00:41:29,041 --> 00:41:33,583
what’s wrong with
what organisation,

554
00:41:33,834 --> 00:41:37,875
with each evil man,
evildoer.

555
00:41:38,041 --> 00:41:41,458
It will be… the best
way is to meditate.

556
00:41:41,667 --> 00:41:43,625
Not to be aggressive
in any way.

557
00:41:43,834 --> 00:41:48,542
But just to meditate and
ask Mahakali: “Destroy!

558
00:41:48,834 --> 00:41:53,083
Destroy him, for he is destroying
the world. You please destroy him!”

559
00:41:53,291 --> 00:41:55,542
That’s Her job and
She’d love to do it,

560
00:41:55,750 --> 00:41:58,542
but somebody has to
tell Her and ask Her.

561
00:41:58,792 --> 00:42:01,917
It’s very good, because
there are so many,

562
00:42:02,083 --> 00:42:04,458
that unless and until
you point it out,

563
00:42:04,709 --> 00:42:07,917
She may not be able to put Her
attention to that - possibly.

564
00:42:08,083 --> 00:42:12,583
So it’s best is always
ask Her to help you.

565
00:42:12,792 --> 00:42:16,375
On individual basis.
On a national basis.

566
00:42:16,583 --> 00:42:21,333
Maybe on a collective basis
or maybe on a global basis.

567
00:42:21,542 --> 00:42:26,625
That’s what. She exists everywhere.
She is globally available.

568
00:42:26,875 --> 00:42:28,875
Anywhere: you may
be having

569
00:42:29,041 --> 00:42:33,792
any colour, any race,
any nation - anything.

570
00:42:33,999 --> 00:42:37,667
but She exists within
you all the time.

571
00:42:37,875 --> 00:42:41,375
And to worship Her
and to awaken Her,

572
00:42:41,625 --> 00:42:45,458
is only ‘your’ due,
that ‘you’ have to do.

573
00:42:45,667 --> 00:42:49,000
If She is awakened within you,
you’ll be a humble person.

574
00:42:49,208 --> 00:42:51,834
You will see what mistakes
you have been committing

575
00:42:52,041 --> 00:42:55,542
and you’ll feel bad about it.
You will not feel ‘guilty’,

576
00:42:55,792 --> 00:42:56,750
but you will feel ‘bad’,

577
00:42:56,999 --> 00:42:59,959
that: I will never do such a thing.
I have done very great wrong.

578
00:43:00,125 --> 00:43:02,417
And then you will
try to correct it.

579
00:43:02,667 --> 00:43:05,083
All this works out

580
00:43:05,291 --> 00:43:09,000
very well when you are
pure in your heart.

581
00:43:09,250 --> 00:43:13,417
Your heart should be pure.
If your heart is not pure,

582
00:43:13,625 --> 00:43:20,875
if you are doing Sahaja Yoga to
have some competition with others

583
00:43:21,041 --> 00:43:26,083
or with some sort of material
achievements, it will not work out.

584
00:43:26,458 --> 00:43:31,875
You have to do it in a way
that is an innocent act,

585
00:43:32,208 --> 00:43:35,667
that you are worshipping your
Mother like a little child

586
00:43:35,875 --> 00:43:37,709
worships and loves
his mother.

587
00:43:37,959 --> 00:43:41,792
It’s a very simple relationship,
which all of us have felt,

588
00:43:42,000 --> 00:43:44,709
how we should love
our Mother and

589
00:43:44,959 --> 00:43:50,333
how we should be under Her
guidance and under Her protection.

590
00:43:50,583 --> 00:43:54,208
That is something very simple you
have known in your childhood

591
00:43:54,458 --> 00:43:57,333
and that childhood has
to come back in you

592
00:43:57,542 --> 00:44:00,375
if you really
worship the Mother.

593
00:44:00,667 --> 00:44:03,834
May God Bless you.

